text: Heteroclytomorpha sormeoides is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1908.BioLib.cz - Heteroclytomorpha sormeoides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Subspecies== * Heteroclytomorpha sormeoides ammiralis Breuning, 1956 * Heteroclytomorpha sormeoides salomonum Breuning, 1950 * Heteroclytomorpha sormeoides sormeoides Aurivillius, 1908 ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1908
title: Heteroclytomorpha sormeoides
